s home in The Netherlands so he could dial in the perfect start.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands.jpg\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands.jpg\" alt=\"Olympic BMX prototype 2-speed derailleur gears Meybo bike, BMX World Champion Twan van Gendt, Red Bull ramp\" width=\"1440\" height=\"800\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands.jpg 1440w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands-297x165.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands-800x444.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands-120x67.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/22115746/Olympic-BMX-prototype-2-speed-derailleur-gears-Meybo-bike_BMX-World-Champion-Twan-van-Gendt_training-start-ramp-The-Netherlands-768x427.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.co